## Design Rules

- Dark background (`#141413`) is the default — commit to it
- Claude Orange (`#d97757`) is the primary accent — use it for anything that needs to pop
- Never use bright white (`#ffffff`) — use warm off-white (`#faf9f5`) instead
- One accent color per slide dominates — don't split equally between orange and blue
- "People + AI = Power Moves" appears on every slide/footer

